dc_description_s: This data represents zoning for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2022 and includes the layers 'Portage_General_2022,' and 'Portage_Shoreland_2022.' [Shoreland: Polygon data depicting shoreland zone for lakes and impoundments. Water bodies are included if they have a history of holding water in 2000, 2005, 2010 Portage County Aerial photography.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.portage.wi.us/department/planning-zoning/land-information-gis/maps-and-gis-data
